         <abstract>Lillian McCredy Duke was the first wife of James B. Duke.  The two were married in 1904 and divorced in 1906.  The papers in this collection are related to the divorce proceedings. The materials in this collection contain correspondence, newspaper clippings, case exhibits, trial transcripts, and envelopes.  The material ranges in date from 1904-1906.</abstract>
         
