               <p>The Clippings series contains newspaper clippings taken from various newspapers and were compiled by a clipping service of Ben B. Hampton and Co., New York.  The bulk of the clippings are from May 1906.  The clippings include excerpts from the trial proceedings and testimony of one of the chief witnesses, Lillian Duke's former servant Miss Sands.</p>
            
            
